1. Character Card Specification (chara_card_v2 / chara_card_v3)
-------------------------------------------------------------------------------

The character card JSON format ("chara_card_v2" and "chara_card_v3") is a
community specification originated by the SillyTavern project:

  Source: https://github.com/SillyTavern/SillyTavern
  Specification: https://github.com/malfoyslastname/character-card-spec-v2

TavernOS implements read/write compatibility with this format for
interoperability with the broader character card ecosystem. The specification
itself is not affiliated with, endorsed by, or sponsored by TavernOS.

"SillyTavern" is a trademark of its respective owners. TavernOS is an
independent project and is not derived from or based on SillyTavern source
code.

