4. LLM Provider APIs
-------------------------------------------------------------------------------

TavernOS integrates with multiple LLM provider APIs. These providers are
independent services and are not affiliated with TavernOS:

  - OpenAI             (https://openai.com)
  - Moonshot / Kimi    (https://moonshot.cn)
  - Zhipu / GLM        (https://zhipuai.cn)
  - DeepSeek           (https://deepseek.com)
  - Yunwu              (https://yunwu.ai)
  - xAI / Grok         (https://x.ai)
  - OpenRouter         (https://openrouter.ai)
  - Ollama             (https://ollama.ai)

API keys and credentials are stored locally and are never transmitted to
any server other than the respective provider's API endpoint.
